scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents note
scopecontent.p: Includes Old Burnside research and fragments (p. 1-13, 17-33, and 69-130), fiction fragment with characters named Kate, Louise, Beard, Miss Beulah Ballou, and Lulu Ballou (p. 14-16 and 34-68), and fiction fragment with character named Maggie (p. 131-142).
